A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Real Property – Residential Foreclosures – Materially Delinquent Mortgages
3 FOR the purpose of altering certain requirements for an order to docket or a complaint to
4 foreclose a mortgage or deed of trust on residential property; requiring a secured
5 party to provide certain loan–related correspondence in order to enforce a materially
6 delinquent mortgage, subject to certain exceptions; permitting a mortgagor to raise
7 a defense of laches in an action to enforce a materially delinquent mortgage; and
8 generally relating to materially delinquent mortgages and foreclosures on
9 residential property.
